snippet.title: Baby Classical ⚡ SCHUBERT, CHOPIN & BACH ⚡ Piano Music for Babies
snippet.description:
Classical music full of tenderness from wonderful composers like Schubert, Chopin, and Bach, lovingly chosen to help your baby sleep peacefully and happily. Perfect for a moment of calm and cuddles before bedtime.

We hope you enjoy it!

00:00 2 German Dances D.769​ - F. Schubert
​02:18 3 German Dances D.972​ - F. Schubert
​05:23 8 Ecossaises D.977​ - F. Schubert
​11:47 8 Ländler D.37​8​ - F. Schubert
08:18 Impromptu D.946 - II​ - F. Schubert
21:00 Waltz in G Major D.844 'Albumblatt'​ - F. Schubert
22:02 Nocturne  in E-flat major - Op. 9 No. 2 - F. Chopin
26:28 Nocturne No. 20 in C♯ minor, Op. posth. Lento con gran espressione - F. Chopin
30:47 Nocturne Op. 37 No.1 - F. Chopin
38:15 Polonaise in G minor Op. Posth (B1 KK lla No.1) - F. Chopin
42:11 Waltz - Op.64 No.1 - F. Chopin
44:40 Waltz - Op.64 No.2 - F. Chopin
49:52 Waltz - Op.64 No.3 - F. Chopin
55:03 Waltz - Op.69 No.1 - F. Chopin
01:00:18 Goldberg Variations BWV 988 (Aria) - J. S. Bach
01:05:00 Invention No.1 in C Major BWV 772 - J. S. Bach
01:06:33 Invention No.4 in D Minor BWV 775 - J. S. Bach
01:08:07 Minuet in C Minor BWV Anh. 121 - J. S. Bach
01:09:17 Minuet in F Major BWV Anh. 118 - J. S. Bach
01:11:00 Minuet in G Major BWV Anh. 114 - J. S. Bach
01:12:35 Minuet in G Major BWV Anh. 116 - J. S. Bach
01:14:46 Minuet in G Minor BWV Anh. 115 - J. S. Bach
01:16:27 Polonaise in F Major BWV Anh. 117a - J. S. Bach
01:18:21 Rondeau in B Flat Major BWV Anh. 183 - Fr. Couperin - J. S. Bach
